00:01:21.540 --> 00:01:23.380
Has news from Liangzhou arrived?

00:01:25.100 --> 00:01:27.620
Yes. Liangzhou is suffering
a severe drought.

00:01:27.660 --> 00:01:29.619
Prefect Jiang Liantang
concealed it from the court.

00:01:29.620 --> 00:01:31.540
Bandits have risen
in revolt because of it.

00:01:31.700 --> 00:01:33.420
The disaster can no longer be hidden.

00:01:33.700 --> 00:01:34.820
Young Lady Su.

00:01:35.180 --> 00:01:36.740
I came today

00:01:36.780 --> 00:01:38.660
to ask you to keep your promise.

00:01:42.780 --> 00:01:44.580
These are all the grains we purchased.

00:01:45.580 --> 00:01:47.540
And what about your promise
to me, Your Lordship?

00:01:47.862 --> 00:01:49.222
At this morning's court assembly,

00:01:49.525 --> 00:01:50.711
His Majesty has appointed me

00:01:50.712 --> 00:01:52.540
General of Relief and Pacification.

00:01:52.700 --> 00:01:54.020
I depart tomorrow.

00:01:55.537 --> 00:01:57.657
I only thought you
would handle disaster relief,

00:01:58.125 --> 00:01:59.932
but now you must also quell rebellion.

00:02:01.787 --> 00:02:04.786
Disaster relief
wins the people's hearts,

00:02:04.787 --> 00:02:05.947
and quelling the rebellion

00:02:05.980 --> 00:02:07.340
secures military power.

00:02:10.220 --> 00:02:11.700
You said once

00:02:12.060 --> 00:02:14.180
this would be
Xiao Manor's greatest chance.

00:02:22.740 --> 00:02:24.100
A fine account indeed.

00:02:24.940 --> 00:02:26.340
Young Lady Su.

00:02:26.750 --> 00:02:27.536
My residence

00:02:27.537 --> 00:02:29.380
lacks a mistress like you.

00:02:31.487 --> 00:02:32.936
Would you consider it?

00:02:32.937 --> 00:02:33.897
Qi Sheng.

00:02:34.740 --> 00:02:36.139
Relief affairs are settled.

00:02:36.140 --> 00:02:37.340
You may leave now.

00:02:39.525 --> 00:02:40.685
Yan.

00:02:40.700 --> 00:02:42.420
I mean what I say.

00:02:43.060 --> 00:02:44.859
Young Lady Su is in her prime,

00:02:44.860 --> 00:02:46.220
gentle and capable.

00:02:46.387 --> 00:02:48.760
If she keeps watch over
your brother's tablet for a lifetime,

00:02:48.760 --> 00:02:49.867
would it not be a pity?

00:02:55.550 --> 00:02:56.550
Young Lady Su,

00:02:56.825 --> 00:02:58.625
give it some serious thought.

00:02:58.687 --> 00:03:00.059
We have been

00:03:00.060 --> 00:03:01.139
through much together,

00:03:01.140 --> 00:03:02.259
we know each other well.

00:03:02.260 --> 00:03:03.580
Your Lordship, mind your words.

00:03:03.912 --> 00:03:06.072
I will forever
be the wife of Xiao Yunxi.

00:03:15.525 --> 00:03:19.499
(Xiao Manor)

00:03:19.500 --> 00:03:20.499
Yan.

00:03:20.500 --> 00:03:22.460
You must return safely.

00:03:22.580 --> 00:03:23.700
Take good care.

00:03:23.900 --> 00:03:26.300
Yan, we will wait for you to come home.

00:03:29.460 --> 00:03:30.870
Travel safely.

00:03:40.262 --> 00:03:42.482
(Xiao Manor)

00:03:53.260 --> 00:03:54.500
Let us go.

00:03:55.620 --> 00:03:56.700
Let us go.

