(Xiao Manor)

00:04:16.850 --> 00:04:18.695
(Xiao Manor)

00:04:27.700 --> 00:04:30.060
Xie Yunyan.

00:04:34.380 --> 00:04:35.620
Xie Yunyan.

00:04:57.300 --> 00:04:59.180
I thought you would not come.

00:05:02.100 --> 00:05:03.340
Xie Yunyan.

00:05:06.180 --> 00:05:07.860
Stay well.

00:05:08.300 --> 00:05:09.620
Come back safe.

00:05:10.637 --> 00:05:12.157
I will wait for you at home.

00:05:17.820 --> 00:05:18.980
Alright.

00:05:40.275 --> 00:05:46.286
(Xiao Manor)

00:05:46.287 --> 00:05:48.286
Su Jinyuan. You ruined my entire family.

00:05:48.287 --> 00:05:49.139
I will kill you.

00:05:49.140 --> 00:05:50.074
Su Xinyue.

00:05:50.075 --> 00:05:51.739
What nonsense are you spouting again?

00:05:51.740 --> 00:05:53.819
If you had not
seized the Su family's property,

00:05:53.820 --> 00:05:56.180
I would never have pushed
my parents to hoard grain.

00:05:56.500 --> 00:05:58.539
My mother would not have
borrowed from lenders.

00:05:58.540 --> 00:06:00.460
And they would not have been arrested.

00:06:01.162 --> 00:06:02.540
If they die,

00:06:02.780 --> 00:06:04.557
you will be buried with them.

00:06:05.812 --> 00:06:07.524
Was it I who told you to drive up prices

00:06:07.525 --> 00:06:08.925
and profit off disaster?

00:06:12.820 --> 00:06:14.220
I will kill you.

00:06:15.725 --> 00:06:17.957
(Xiao Manor)

00:06:18.980 --> 00:06:20.260
Are you alright?

00:06:24.980 --> 00:06:27.545
How about her? Do you want
to report it to the authorities?

00:06:28.820 --> 00:06:29.582
Forget it.

00:06:29.980 --> 00:06:30.859
Right now,

00:06:30.860 --> 00:06:32.740
she is suffering more than death itself.

00:06:34.812 --> 00:06:35.986
Thank you, Sir.

00:06:35.987 --> 00:06:37.547
May I know the name of my rescuer?

00:06:46.675 --> 00:06:48.211
Sir.

00:06:48.212 --> 00:06:49.379
I cannot explain why,

00:06:49.380 --> 00:06:51.100
but you feel familiar to me.

00:06:54.060 --> 00:06:55.180
I'm leaving.

00:06:57.037 --> 00:06:59.595
(Xiao Manor)

00:07:07.260 --> 00:07:08.380
Xiao Yunxi.

00:07:12.912 --> 00:07:14.912
If you truly
cannot let go of Su Jinyuan,

00:07:15.180 --> 00:07:17.060
take off your mask and face her.

00:07:25.820 --> 00:07:27.140
Being able to watch over her

00:07:27.587 --> 00:07:28.699
is already enough for me.

00:07:28.700 --> 00:07:29.557
You...

00:07:31.980 --> 00:07:33.459
Every time,

00:07:33.460 --> 00:07:35.300
it feels like punching cotton.

00:07:51.060 --> 00:07:52.180
Apothecary.

00:07:52.300 --> 00:07:54.300
Is the ginseng soup
Physician Xi mentioned ready?

00:07:55.220 --> 00:07:56.420
It is ready.

00:07:57.300 --> 00:07:58.507
Sir.

00:07:59.660 --> 00:08:00.700
It was you, was it not?

00:08:04.300 --> 00:08:05.300
Soak it first.

00:08:25.900 --> 00:08:27.299
This is burn ointment.

00:08:27.300 --> 00:08:28.099
Apply it quickly,

00:08:28.100 --> 00:08:29.140
