00:10:02.140 --> 00:10:03.940
Jingyi sounds lovely.

00:10:04.020 --> 00:10:05.445
Jingyi.

00:10:05.580 --> 00:10:06.739
A fine name.

00:10:06.740 --> 00:10:07.660
Yes.

00:10:08.180 --> 00:10:10.460
I will add it
to the family record later.

00:10:10.500 --> 00:10:13.299
